{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0001", "text": "不要哭 並無做錯事 動情沒有不對", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 4, 3, 2, 0, 2, 4, 2, 2, 0, 2, 5, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "jiu3", "huk1", "bing6", "mou4", "zou6", "co3", "si6", "dung6", "cing4", "mut6", "jau5", "bat1", "deoi3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "並", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做錯事", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "動情", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0002", "text": "要是錯 錯在難共你 天生一對", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 4, 4, 2, 0, 2, 5, 3, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jiu3", "si6", "co3", "co3", "zoi6", "naan4", "gung6", "nei5", "tin1", "sang1", "jat1", "deoi3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "要是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "錯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "錯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "難", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "共", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天生一對", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0003", "text": "給我的 轉送下個吧 不要浪費你眼淚", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 5, 3, 9, 4, 2, 4, 2, 3, 4, 2, 4, 5, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["kap1", "ngo5", "dik1", "zyun2", "sung3", "haa6", "go3", "baa6", "bat1", "jiu3", "long6", "fai3", "nei5", "ngaan5", "leoi6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "轉送", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "下個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "浪費", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "眼淚", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0004", "text": "老實說 爲了怎麼婉拒 我都連夜也沒有睡", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 4, 5, 9, 3, 9, 5, 5, 3, 0, 2, 5, 2, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["lou5", "sat6", "syut3", "liu5", "zam2", "mo1", "jyun2", "keoi5", "ngo5", "dou1", "lin4", "je6", "jaa5", "mut6", "jau5", "seoi6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "老實", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "婉拒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "連夜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "睡", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0005", "text": "難得 有人待我這麼好", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 5, 0, 2, 5, 5, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["naan4", "dak1", "jau5", "jan4", "doi6", "ngo5", "ze5", "mo1", "hou2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "難得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "待", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0006", "text": "如此照料周到 何事我又要讓人 最苦惱", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 4, 2, 3, 4, 0, 2, 5, 2, 4, 2, 0, 4, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "ci2", "ziu3", "liu6", "zau1", "dou3", "ho4", "si6", "ngo5", "jau6", "jiu3", "joeng6", "jan4", "zeoi3", "fu2", "nou5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如此", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "照料", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "周到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "何事", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "讓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "苦惱", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0007", "text": "明明知 有人待我這麼好", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 3, 5, 0, 2, 5, 5, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ming4", "ming4", "zi1", "jau5", "jan4", "doi6", "ngo5", "ze5", "mo1", "hou2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "明明", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "待", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0008", "text": "如沒有信心接受到 難道詐不知道比較好", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 4, 3, 4, 2, 4, 0, 2, 4, 3, 3, 2, 9, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "mut6", "jau5", "seon3", "sam1", "zip3", "sau6", "dou3", "naan4", "dou6", "zaa3", "bat1", "zi1", "dou6", "bei2", "gaau3", "hou2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "信心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "接受", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "難道", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "詐", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "知道", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比較", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0009", "text": "或者可以好友般 跳陣舞", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 9, 9, 5, 9, 5, 3, 4, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waak6", "ze2", "ho2", "ji5", "hou2", "jau5", "bun1", "tiu3", "zan6", "mou5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "或者", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好友", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "般", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跳陣舞", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0010", "text": "怎去講 極殘酷說話 並無字眼恰當", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 4, 9, 2, 0, 2, 4, 2, 2, 0, 2, 5, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zam2", "heoi3", "gong2", "gik6", "caan4", "huk6", "syut3", "waa6", "bing6", "mou4", "zi6", "ngaan5", "hap1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "怎去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "講", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "極", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "殘酷", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說話", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "並", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "字眼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "恰當", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人", "artists": ["麥浚龍"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1746", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_MTc0Ng_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
